div.div:
MainController's initialization
involves creating and configuring several critical Angular providers, as well as the subview controllers: CleanController, AnalyzeController and VisualizeController. The latter two controllers will be omitted from this diagram.

div.style: display: inline-block; font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.2; vertical-align: top; width: 199px; white-space: normal;
div.div:
session's initialization involves
creating and initializing the
socketConnection provider which establishes a WebSocket connection with the Willow backend through SocketIO. It then tests that the [sessionID] is valid by sending a test WebSocket request (metadata).

(first fifty rows and first ten columns) in the data table.
